This deck needs to have two file with it TheBack.Ilbm and TheBrush.Grab.
They need to be in the same directory as the deck.

1. Start deck
2. There are four buttons on this screen.
   They are the following (starting from the top and going down).
     QUIT  : Quit the deck.
     
     CLEAR : Restore the background of the card.
             This will remove any rendering (drawing) that may be on the
             screen.
             
     OFF   : This is the transparency status.
             Pressing this button will toggle between Transparent ON
             and Transparent OFF.  The minterms act differently depending
             on the transparent status.
             
     DO IT : This will render TheBrush.Grab onto various locations of
             the screen with various minterm values.  See following chart:

